originalText.text: Very unprofessional, I requested a NIPT test to be done and because I declined all other blood work she got upset and said it’s all or none that she wouldn’t do the NIPT testing for me if I didn’t do the other blood work. Now refuses to put it in my chart accurately instead she wrote that I refused lab works and failed to mention her unprofessional comments aside from the fact that that is untrue and not legal and tried to bring up the fact that I was late like that had to do with anything. Some people in the medical field are just completely unaware that some patients actually know their rights but it’s ok. I will no longer be in her care. Just a warning to others of her ignorance and unprofessionalism. Trying to intimidate a patient into doing what she wants by refusing to do blood work and stating completely false comments about how legally I have to when I know for a fact I don’t.
